Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拔出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 修呢嘛呢嘛嘛呢 嘛呢修修呢 娑婆訶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個怪物已經不是人類能打倒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們約定過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要證明獅郎救你是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在去證明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你缺少的只是自信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去奪取自己的容身之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這東西 要怎麼打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看來沒這麼容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:07.47,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,517)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(412,605)}光輝燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}結界破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瘴氣要散播到城市裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 多虧了這場大雨 抑制了孢子的擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少現在抑制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然沒能撐住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}地獄之門開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不中用的人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瘴氣洩露到外面去可就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和怪物戰鬥的驅魔師們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}送你們尼采的「善惡的彼岸」中的一句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「與怪物戰鬥之人 應當小心自己不要變成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為當你凝視深淵之時 深淵也在凝視你」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒想到他的再生能力如此之強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都告訴你別小瞧伽樓羅的再生能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然 現在的你們是殺不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽樓羅的能力我也基本掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}該撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但在撤退之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村雪男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我對你很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「我討厭自己」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是幼稚的自我否定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是墮為惡魔的第一步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別把我和你相提並論 惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惡魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對了 他是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我把驅魔術最基礎的東西忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能聽從惡魔的花言巧語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在這樣的大雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}水精的魔法彈應該能發揮出平時兩三倍的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必須冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你哥哥明明也是惡魔 你為什麼這麼抗拒惡魔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惡魔有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也有當惡魔的潛力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來 再讓我看一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}堅決不當惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩同學 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後問你一遍 人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底是誰 有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不錯 你的表情真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是惡魔的表情 這就是你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但你還差得很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可不會告訴現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起這個 大家能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他馬上就會復活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們還是放棄抓捕他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在要全力逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大部隊在那個火焰結界裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}結界崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁現在雨水壓制了瘴氣 我們趕緊去匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓緊時間和大部隊匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是惡魔的表情 這就是你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}窺探深淵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到底是為了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惡 惡魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惡魔 天使 明王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這些不過是人類擅自給我取的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身纏神之火焰的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是不淨潔金剛 烏樞沙摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王是我長年的宿敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那把劍本是我們首領的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你若想打倒不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可以教你操縱火焰的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但拜託了 烏樞沙摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟著我詠唱真言和佛經
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}召喚火生三昧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒想到能看到青色的烏樞沙摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔劍原本就是用以寄宿「不動」之尊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可供佛教系的火焰惡魔依附的魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使它寄宿著奧村的惡魔心臟 也沒有失去這個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然是意想不到的發展 但這樣也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火生三昧能燒盡物質界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再加上你這魔神的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能把不淨王連同這座山一起 整個燃燒殆盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和山一起燃燒殆盡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡還有很多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那又怎樣 不必在意這種小事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}進入不淨王之城的人 以及其爪牙所碰觸之人都會被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必須一個不漏地淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要有漏網之魚 不淨王就會再度復活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打倒不淨王卻不能傷到別人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒時間磨蹭了 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修呢嘛呢嘛嘛呢 嘛呢修修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真言很清晰地浮現在了腦海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 俱嚕馱曩 吽伽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喊出佛經的同時放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火生三昧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再注入更多力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要 要是再注入更多力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的理智就要被火焰吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 我的力量比不上菌的繁殖力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能親自把神木同學拉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小尼 能不能把我舉上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夠了 你太沒分寸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你驅使惡魔過度了 會死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我最討厭你了 所以別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論你怎麼看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只要這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 杜山詩惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨蛋 你真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算你討厭我 我也最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不能磨蹭了 得快點把師父送下山…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個藍色的光是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個形狀 是火生三昧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和我召喚出來的完全不是一個級別的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那裡發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要被火焰吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從出生起 我的力量就一直被抑制著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我受夠了 我是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要摧毀一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燒燬一切的野獸就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}詩惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 我一點都沒有被燒傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都相信著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能辜負他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全員撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}青色的火焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是吧 來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼可能沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火焰只將菌系淨化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個火焰到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王的飛沫正在消失 能看到地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們到裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走吧 子貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們兩個 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還能動的跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}名副其實的「送靈火」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身負殺害同門的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}青之驅魔師誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}淨化結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你終將做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂 修拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}做 做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我控制住火焰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然細節方面還有很多不足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我有自信能區分能燒和不能燒的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓 志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓丸 我終於能控制力量了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我控制住了 沒有燒到不淨王以外的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過真是一次奇妙的體驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在火焰中竟然不痛也不癢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}包括我在內 被瘴氣感染的人都被淨化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在青色的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是強大的力量 不知該怎麼感謝你才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被你這樣表揚我多不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村同學 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為 為什麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓你真是想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還以為你死掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.07,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧 奧村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.56,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等… 別摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是雪男啊 你也沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 為什麼我哥哥會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰把他從牢裡放出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以嘛 不是跟你道過歉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣雪男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是救了這裡的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓你驚訝到下巴脫臼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超過你的日子也不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}開什麼玩笑 你知道自己的狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然還是撒旦之子 無法逃避這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直都害怕面對 害怕承認
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這也是我 雪男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是不能承認這個力量 我就無法前進
